♪ Good gracious,
ass is bodacious ♪

11:38.698 --> 11:39.829
- ♪ Ooh
- ♪ Flirtatious

11:39.873 --> 11:41.135
♪ Trying to make faces

11:41.178 --> 11:43.093
- ♪ Ooh
- [laughs]

11:43.137 --> 11:45.052
What's going on with you?

11:45.095 --> 11:47.358
- I don't know.
